  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/2ec5ee8be1757301.jpg?v=1782539233\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>It's that time once again - the 22nd of the month. Some of the Garden Girls from <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/whats-hot/%3Fpp%3D300\">Two Peas In A Bucket</a> are doing a little blog hop.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/23c08581d1517196.jpg?v=1782539236\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/be287a1f94a4dbb6.jpg?v=1782539239\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>How cute are those little <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/lawn-fawn/115623-clear-to-see-clear-stamps/%3Ffilters%3D_lawn_fawn_\">glasses by Lawn Fawn</a>?</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/59b75b25de0d502e.jpg?v=1782539242\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>1. This awesome <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/mama-elephant/137854-trifecta-stamps/\">stamp set by Mama Elephant</a></p><p>2. <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/echo-park-paper-co/137141-one-day-12x12-vol-1-paper/%3Ffilters%3Dwhats-hot\">This paper</a> = perfect for Project Life.</p><p>3. <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/hero-arts/138049-hello-bubble-wood-block-stamp/%3Ffilters%3Dlast-30-days\">Hero Arts Hello woodblock stamp</a></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/7d87d50e7cec1b0f.jpg?v=1782539244\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>4. <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/hero-arts/138028-charcoal-mid-tone-shadow-ink-pad/%3Ffilters%3Dlast-30-days\">Hero Arts Charcoal Shadow Ink</a></p><p>5. <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/technique-tuesday/137859-be-mine-january-studio-ae-clear-stamp-limited-edition/%3Ffilters%3Dlast-30-days\">Be Mine stamp set</a></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/5f09fd429cf45376.jpg?v=1782539247\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>This adorable layout by adogslife13 with cool stitched chevron elements.Next stop on the hop is <a href=\"http://www.wilnaf.com/\">Wilna</a>. Remember you can always check the <a href=\"http://twopeasinabucket.typepad.com/\">Two Peas blog</a> for the entire list of participants.</p>"
